            repairs;

Allows the use of non-local maintenance and diagnostic tools only as consistent with
            organizational policy and documented in the security plan for the information
            system;

Maintenance personnel notify [Assignment: organization-defined
                  personnel] when non-local maintenance is planned (i.e., date/time);
                and

